{"type": "article", "id": 19691, "title": "带簸箕和刷子的垃圾桶", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-25T07:00:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607131341aQgIdDlV1zxS9moZ.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是韩国设计师 Yoon So Young 带来的垃圾桶，将簸箕和刷子巧妙安置在垃圾桶上，想要解决清洁工具占空间的问题。簸箕充当了垃圾桶的盖子，两侧凸出来了圆扣刚好挂在垃圾桶边缘空出的圆孔里，然后以圆扣做轴，成为一个可以前后旋转的翻盖垃圾桶。刷子也贴边悬挂着，拿取都很方便。这个设计获得今年的红点奖，<a href=\"http://www.red-dot.sg/zh/online-exhibition/3-in-1-bin/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150124ICLs5QEhtuJRwZgi.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"1485\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.41428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150124PFyeVp8w9hUkC51D.jpg\" width=\"234\" height=\"186\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.79487179\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}